title: About
text:
Hello and welcome to my webpage! My name is Jenevieve and I’m delighted to have you here.
I am a Year 1 Communications and New Media major with a minor in Interactive Media Development. This webpage serves as a platform for me to share my journey, insights and projects with you.
Thank you for visiting!💟

Rediscover Harry Potter Through Data
Traverse the magical landscape of J.K. Rowling’s beloved series, reimagined through data⚡. Through immersive data visualisations and insightful analysis, this project aims to unveil the hidden depths and captivating characters that define Rowling’s masterpiece, offering fresh perspectives and newfound appreciation for the wizarding world of Harry Potter.
